rows.label: qev041603_MSG0001
rows.name:
Welcome to general store of Nana!
What is friend needing today?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Hmm? Friend wants information on thief who stole
cargo from courier?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0003
rows.name:
Well, Nana saw huge thing that rumbled the ground
as it came running.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0004
rows.name:
It has to be slithery snitching snake of rumors!
Also, it breathe fire just like stories say.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0005
rows.name:
Nana was worried it would cart off entire general
store, but it didn't.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0006
rows.name:
Still, Nana lucky to be alive. Extremely fortunate.
Basically miraculous, really.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0007
rows.name:
Regardless, better to lose some stock and stay alive.
Probably best to start looking for next mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0008
rows.name:
Nana strongly recommend friend give up trying to
chase down huge thief thing. Much too dangerous.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0009
rows.name: There are two types of friends in this world.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0010
rows.name: Friends who make money, and friends who lose it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0011
rows.name:
Money type make money all their life,
but lose out in everything else.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0012
rows.name:
Type who lose money get used by those who make it,
but outside business are better than money type.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0013
rows.name: Hard to say who is happier.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0014
rows.name: Welcome to general store of Nana![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0015
rows.name: Oh, hello again. Is business of friend going well?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0017
rows.name:
Very impressive. Nana knew friend was the type who
makes money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041603_MSG0018
rows.name:
Next time friend has lead on making more money,
Nana hope friend will drop by and share.[ST:wait ]
